title": "2021/10/25 21:00 GMT", "description": "The latest five minute news bulletin from BBC World Service.", "url": "https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/w172xzjsyzr53qn", "urlToImage": "https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/1200x675/p060dh18.jpg", "publishedAt": "2021-10-25T21:06:00Z", "content": "The latest five minute news bulletin from BBC World Service."}, {"source": {"id": "bbc-news", "name": "BBC News"}, "author": "https://www.facebook.com/bbcnews", "title": "Sudan coup: Three protesters killed and dozens injured", "description": "Soldiers are said to have opened fire on large crowds opposing the military takeover.", "url": "https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-59045020", "urlToImage": "https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/1024/branded_news/0FFB/production/_121219040_khartoumgetty.jpg", "publishedAt": "2021-10-25T20:56:00Z", "content": "Media caption, Demonstrators take to the streets of Khartoum to protest against the arrests\r\nAt least three people are reported to have died and dozens more have been hurt after soldiers fired on cro\u2026 [+3737 chars]"}, {"source": {"id": "bbc-news", "name": "BBC News"}, "author": "https://www.facebook.com/bbcnews", "title": "Bibaa Henry and Nicole Smallman: Met Police to apologise to family of murdered sisters", "description": "Met Police Commissioner Cressida Dick says a better response would have saved \"immeasurable pain\".", "url": "https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-london-59045471", "urlToImage": "https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/1024/branded_news/11EB5/production/_118879337_p22bhns52.jpg", "publishedAt": "2021-10-25T20:40:52Z", "content": "Image source, Henry/Smallman family\r\nImage caption, Sisters Bibaa Henry (left) and Nicole Smallman were found in bushes by friends\r\nThe Metropolitan Police will apologise to the family of two murdere\u2026 [+1430 chars]"}, {"source": {"id": "bbc-news", "name": "BBC News"}, "author": "https://www.facebook.com/bbcnews", "title": "Man rescued from rocks after kayak capsizes on Solway Coa